    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>通过一场梦境体验这场恐龙岛的旅行</strong></h2>这是一部休闲、解谜、探索向的独立游戏，您将在游戏中通过操控慈母龙妈妈，以找寻自己的三个宝宝为目的来完成这场梦境旅行。在这场寻子冒险之中，您将会看到恐龙岛上海岸、平原、森林、沼泽、溪谷、高山等地貌的场景。其中将会有十余种恐龙对您的冒险进行帮助或阻碍，您需要通过交付对应的谜题任务来克服一个个难关。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669930/extras/d6a218e303a4fd74c4f95aa674cf2702.poster.avif?t=1633664243\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669930/extras/d6a218e303a4fd74c4f95aa674cf2702.webm?t=1633664243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669930/extras/d6a218e303a4fd74c4f95aa674cf2702.mp4?t=1633664243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>表情气泡式交流方式</strong></h2>本作在核心内容上取消了文字气泡，采用了类似表情包式的结构。这种方式可以避免让您得到文字带来的强提示性，通过表情气泡式的方式保留了一定的猜谜空间。您完全可以在游戏前期通过一些表情的共性找到一些表情气泡谜语中暗含的规律。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669930/extras/0168bdca4c62df3d50359e542833fa6d.poster.avif?t=1633664243\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669930/extras/0168bdca4c62df3d50359e542833fa6d.webm?t=1633664243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669930/extras/0168bdca4c62df3d50359e542833fa6d.mp4?t=1633664243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>试着通过鼠标的状态来探索一下谜题！</strong></h2>当您发现难以破解谜题时，试着将鼠标在场景中滑动探索一下。通过拾取、调查、交流等鼠标状态来发现场景中可以交互的地方，进而来拼凑成自己线索闭环。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669930/extras/93e70d5c67bf48dbb5b0d10530510910.poster.avif?t=1633664243\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669930/extras/93e70d5c67bf48dbb5b0d10530510910.webm?t=1633664243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669930/extras/93e70d5c67bf48dbb5b0d10530510910.mp4?t=1633664243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>通过休闲小游戏的方式完成任务</strong></h2>有的恐龙在给予您帮助前或者给予您阻碍前，会希望您为他完成一些任务，有可能是会向您索要道具，也可能是会要您去为它做一件事。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669930/extras/3efa4d250fcfb473941faa0687acceaa.poster.avif?t=1633664243\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669930/extras/3efa4d250fcfb473941faa0687acceaa.webm?t=1633664243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669930/extras/3efa4d250fcfb473941faa0687acceaa.mp4?t=1633664243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>制作人有话说</strong></h2>这是一款送给孩子的游戏，爱做梦的小姑娘LiLy在梦中穿越到了白垩纪，自己变成了一只慈母龙妈妈，为了找回被葬火龙偷跑的恐龙宝宝踏上了冒险旅程。本游戏是作者送给亲爱的可爱女儿LiLy的礼物，祝喜欢恐龙的她5岁生日快乐！同时也是送给所有喜欢恐龙的小朋友们的礼物，祝全世界的孩子们开心快乐，健康成长！",
